data.description: Pictures coming soon!!  Welcome to 1217 Clements Bridge in Deptford twp.  This is a 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath with over 1,800 square feet. As soon as you walk in you will see all the renovations that were made for you. It has everything you need. Open layout concept with the living room (with  vaulted ceiling), updated kitchen, and formal dining room. There are 4 bedrooms and 2 full bath on this floor as well. There is also a full unfinished basement with a half bath. Other features include central air, updated plumbing, laundry are on main level, and new floors.
